thread.title: Sinead king

author: Sinead king
title: Sinead king
text: I had encountered problems making a permanent change to my motor policy and requested a callback. My request was dealt with in under an hour by a lovely lady named Danielle who couldn't have been more helpful. Would thoroughly recommend this company to deal with. I'm with them for the last six years and would never consider changing companies due to their competitive prices and professionalism.
